			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Its 3 wolf scales, I am thinkin they are the red ones, tho cant remember (you can often buy these from merchants where other players have sold them for cash).  Do not stack them in the forge.  The water actually messes up the forge and ya lose the coif.  So dont add the water, just combine coif and scales, and the complete coif is all yours.  I only had 1 point in Blacksmithing, and it worked, so I dont know if blacksmithing is a prereq.
				</font>
			</td>

