			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				This is a very easy quest. First u gotta put at least 15 skill points into blacksmithing. Next u talk to the shestar trooper. U then gotta give him 3 loose scales and 5 gold. He them gives u the unfinished coif. U then also have 2 go out and kill scaled wolf hunters and get 3 more loose scales. Then u go 2 the forge provided that u have at least 15 skill points in smithing. U put the scales in the slot and the unfinished coif into the last slot then combine and yer done.
				</font>
